The program gets two numbers and multiplies them together. 

Getting the first number
Enter a number: 5
Getting the second number
Enter a number: 5
The product of your numbers is: 25.

If you try to put a negative number or zero in, it will loop until you put in
the right kind of number.
 
Getting the first number
Enter a number: -3
Enter a number: 4
Getting the second number
Enter a number: 3
The product of your numbers is: 12.

If you try to put in a non-integer value, the program will end.
Getting the first number
Enter a number: 4
Getting the second number
Enter a number: r
The product of your numbers is: 0
